		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-pRgDJ fzXWJx pf-7faee9c1"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="pf-d3927fae"><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-67fbaed6" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-2c51ac69 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-c02b2c51" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-278ebf23"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d642278e">FAQ</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC jHjrlE pf-3a0ec02b"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-4cf38df5 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-bf48f26f accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="0dbf48f2-6f7b-4c4c-b38d-f53c873a0ec0" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Products</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-adae82b0 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="0dbf48f2-6f7b-4c4c-b38d-f53c873a0ec0" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-535226e3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-5cdc5352"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">What makes UMA pads different?</span>&nbsp;</span>For a long time, pads have been made the same way – that is 90% plastic, including the layer coming into contact with your skin. Also for a long time, many of us experience discomfort and irritation (and not to mention the amount of plastic waste!).<br>
<br>At UMA, we believe women deserve something better. That’s why we created a line of period pads using only the highest quality organic ingredients our body deserves.
These pads are wrapped individually in biodegradable film and packed beautifully in fully-recycled boxes.
<br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);"><br></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">What absorbency levels do you offer?</span>&nbsp;</span>UMA is available in Regular and Super size. UMA Regular is 24cm, designed for light to medium flow days. UMA Super is 29cm, designed for heavier flow.&nbsp;<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How often should I change my pads?</span>&nbsp;</span>We recommend changing your pads every 4 to 6 hours depending on your flow. When your flow is heaviest (usually at the beginning of your period), you may want to change more regularly to stay fresh. It is also good to change whenever you feel moisture to avoid bacterial build-up. <br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Can I use these pads for incontinence?</span> </span>Our&nbsp;pads were not designed specifically for incontinence, but some of our customers have used them for light bladder leaks.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(70, 58, 35);"> What does GOTS-certified mean? </span>The Global Organic Textile Standard (GOTS) is recognised as the gold standard of sustainable textile production. It ensures the cotton are&nbsp;grown organically, processed without harmful chemicals, and produced in a way that maintain efficient energy and water consumption, responsible waste management and&nbsp;compliance with International Labour Standard. <br><br><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">What does recycled boxes mean?</span>&nbsp;</span>This means putting back used fibres to the manufacturing system to create new fibres. By extending the lifetime of these fibres, we minimise the amount of waste going to the landfill and the demand for cutting down new trees. Our recycled fibers are certified by the Forest Stewardship Council (FSC).<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Are UMA pads biodegradable?</span>&nbsp;</span>More than 95% component of UMA pads are designed to biodegrade in the landfill, whereas our boxes are 100% biodegradable. Sustainable period care is at the core of our belief. If you are interested in reusable option, join our <span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(161, 100, 76);">waitlist</span> for an exclusive 20% discount on UMA menstrual cup.<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-8df53c87 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f26f7b6c accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="48f26f7b-6c4c-438d-b53c-873a0ec02b2c" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Subscription</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-b5b786b3 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="48f26f7b-6c4c-438d-b53c-873a0ec02b2c" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-ad76d03f"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f991ad76"><br><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">What is UMA subscription?</span> </span>UMA subscription is an automated service that provides you high-quality period care supply wherever and whenever you need it. It saves you from&nbsp;those last-minute pharmacy run!<br><br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);"><span style="font-weight: 700;">How does it work?</span><br></span>STEP ONE: Select your 3-month supply, by following our recommendation or building your own assortment.<br><br>STEP TWO: Complete the payment using credit card or e-Wallets (OVO or GOPAY).<br><br>That's it. Every 3 months, we will replenish your order and send your package of fresh pads.<br><br>P.S. With credit cards, you can enjoy fully-seamless automated payment for your recurring orders. While with e-Wallets, you'll receive a secure payment link for each of your recurring order, and you can authorise the payment with one click.<br>&nbsp;<br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How do I change,&nbsp;skip or cancel my subscription?</span> </span><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">Any modification must be made before the due date</span>. Due to the nature of our automated processing, we cannot modify your subscription or refund your payment once it has been finalised.<br><br>To change your product assortment:<br><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);">[To be updated]</span><span style="text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(208, 2, 27);"><br></span><br>To snooze your subscription:<br><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);">[To be updated]<br><br></span>To cancel your subscription:<br><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);">[To be updated]<br></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How do I update my account info?</span></span><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);"><br></span>Go to Account setting, select 'My Account' section, and update accordingly.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How do I update my shipping info?<br></span>Go to Account setting, select 'Shipping Info' section, and update accordingly.&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">Any modification must be made before the due date</span>. <br><br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">What is my 'Due Date'?<br></span>The date when your next payment is due (i.e. 'Due Date') can be found in your Account setting under 'Subscription' section.<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-3c873a0e accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-7b6c4cf3 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="6f7b6c4c-f38d-453c-873a-0ec02b2c51ac" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Shipping</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-730dbf48 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="6f7b6c4c-f38d-453c-873a-0ec02b2c51ac" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f385de2b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ca62f385"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How much is shipping?</span> </span>Standard shipping is always free with subscription. Without subscription, orders are subject to shipping fees.<br><br><span style="font-weight: 700; color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How long does it take to ship? </span>Standard shipping takes 3 to 5 days, while express shipping takes 1 day.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Where do you ship?</span> </span>We ship nationwide across Indonesia.<br><br><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Can I track my order?</span> </span>Yes. You should receive a notification in your email and SMS whenever your order is dispatched.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">My ordered arrived damaged/is wrong. What should I do?</span>&nbsp;</span>We are sorry this happened.. Email us pictures of your parcel along with your Order ID to <span style="color: rgb(76, 103, 141);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">h</span><span style="font-weight: bold;">e</span><span style="font-weight: bold;">llo@umawomen.com</span></span>. We'll ship you a new one.<br><br><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Do you accept return?</span>&nbsp;</span>We understand that relationships don't always work out. However, given the nature of our products, we cannot accept returns.<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d53f0e51 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-beed9bac accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e3beed9b-acd5-4f0e-91e0-7e247ce953aa" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Payment</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-9bacd53f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e3beed9b-acd5-4f0e-91e0-7e247ce953aa" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c6f75510"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8960c6f7"><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">What forms of payment do you accept?&nbsp;</span>We accept credit cards (VISA, Master Card) and e-Wallets (OVO, GOPAY and LinkAja).<br><br>With credit cards, you can enjoy&nbsp;fully-seamless automated payment for your recurring orders. Whereas with e-Wallets,&nbsp;you will receive a secure payment link for each of your recurring order, and you can authorise the payment with one cli&nbsp;<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-001f667d accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-023a4b40 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b4023a4b-4000-4f66-bdf0-8e6990ace881" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Privacy & Security</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4b40001f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b4023a4b-4000-4f66-bdf0-8e6990ace881" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-6990ace8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f08e6990"><br><b><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Is my card secure?</span> </b>Any sensitive financial data flowing&nbsp;through our system is encrypted by our payment processors (so secure even we cannot see it). For maximum security, we only accept orders from web browsers that allow Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology. This means you cannot inadvertently place an order through an unsecured connection.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">Is my account secure?</span> </span>Your Account will be protected by a password for your privacy and security. To prevent unauthorised access, we recommend protecting your password appropriately and logging out after each use. If you have reason to believe that your account is no longer secure, you should notify us immediately at <span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(76, 103, 141);">hello@umawomen.com</span>.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(70, 58, 35);">How do you use my data?</span>&nbsp;Generally, we use your data to fulfil your orders. This includes scheduling delivery, charging payments and shipment. Occasionally, we also use your contact information to send you updates you’ll probably want to know about, including products, launches, and promos. You can always opt out from these messages by clicking the "unsubscribe" link on the bottom of these emails. From time to time, we may also use aggregated form of users' data to improve your experience. Head to our <span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(76, 103, 141);"><a href="http://umawomen.com/pages/privacy-policy" target="_self" style="">Privacy Policy</a></span> for more in-depth explanation.<br><br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-e953aa26 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-e07e247c accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="51e07e24-7ce9-43aa-a639-bf854de94344" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Partnerships</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-247ce953 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="51e07e24-7ce9-43aa-a63